LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A sturdy door overflowing with literature, entirely illegible.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The teacher's research must pass on.
Insert the Archive Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A sturdy door overflowing with literature, entirely illegible.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The knowledge must be spread.
Insert the Archive Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I'm pretty sure there are words on this, yes these are definitely words.
Key.InvDesc: An ornate key embroidered in scientific inscryption, though it's barely comprehensible.
Key.UsedInvDesc: So many layers of protection, but they must be undone.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: An old door glazed with primal acid.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The rumble of foolery echoes in the distance.
Insert Bardoon's Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: An old door glazed with primal acid.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The wyrm of old slumbers.
Insert Bardoon's Key?

Key.ShopDesc: He seems nice but his neighbors are just the worst.

Key.UsedInvDesc: The way of the fool has been opened.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A decaying door haunted by the lost.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
A kindred spirit's cries for help echo from within.
Insert the Broken Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A prison door of discarded corpses.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Emptiness and regret echo beyond.
Insert the Broken Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Broken? It looks completely functional to me.
Key.InvDesc: A dark key dripping with infection. It looks like it's asking you for help.
Key.UsedInvDesc: Finally bested, a lost soul slumbers in peace.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: An abandoned door, it smells of straw and hoppers.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The keeper awaits, his stories more precious than any 'strength'.
Insert the Buried Geo Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: An old, stone vestibule. It smells of ancient treasure.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The treasure is both far and near.
Insert the Buried Geo Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I better be charging more than 420 for this.
Key.InvDesc: A heavy key beset with an ornate rock. It smells of greed, and betrayal.
Key.UsedInvDesc: The treasure is yours now, may none blame you for it.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A door of repose and study. It's a little slimy.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The merchant awaits in her crooked corner.
Insert the Canyon Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A grand door, etched with the tales of a distant, forgotten city.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The pilgrim's way unfolds.
Insert the Canyon Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Ow! Why is this so receptive to static?
Key.InvDesc: An ornate key with a faint glow. An aura of enlightenment.
Key.UsedInvDesc: The Pilgrim's Way has been opened.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A spongy door overgrown with rich fungus.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The depths of the wastes cry WAH.
Insert the Core Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A dim door, smothered in aged, overgrown fungus.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The bobble of spores echoes beyond.
Insert the Core Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Please get rid of this, it's got something growing on it.
Key.InvDesc: It is overgrown with a rich fungus, and emits a powerful aroma.
Key.UsedInvDesc: The heart of the wastes has been opened.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A crystalline door shining with a forgotten light.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The pilgrimage complete, to dirt we must return.
Insert the Crown Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A crystalline door shining with a forgotten light.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The forgotten one screams from afar, beckoning higher.
Insert the Crown Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Goodness, this one is shiny. Where could it have come from?
Key.InvDesc: Crowned with sharp crystals, it gleams with a forgotten light.
Key.UsedInvDesc: Damned are those who forsake their creator.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A cobblestone door armored in silk.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The skittering never stops.
Insert the Dark Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A cobblestone door armored in silk.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The skittering never stops.
Insert the Dark Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I swear I can't even see this thing without my Lumaflies, it's so black.'
Key.InvDesc: It's dark, thorny, and wrapped in webs. Something out there is angry it's been lost.
Key.UsedInvDesc: You can still hear the skitters, even this far away.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: It looks like it's a locked door but you're not so sure.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The hardest challenge in the game awaits you.
Insert the False Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A rather superfluous door which seems to guard nothing.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Give him time to retrain, he'll be ready.
Insert the False Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I think this is to protect him, not you.
Key.InvDesc: It looks like a key at first, but you can see it's just a casing for a tiny key inside.
Key.UsedInvDesc: If only they possessed the strength they longed for.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A cold, forgotten door, moist in the shadows.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The echo of the songstress calls from afar.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A cold stone door, endlessly dripping.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
You can feel the power of buoyancy calling out to you.
Insert the Flooded Stag Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I don't think this protects anything, just a defunct station?

Finally, something to do with all those relics.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: An ornate door, bespeckled with a collector's wealth.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Rain flows intricately between the carvings.
Insert the Fountain Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Is it destiny you seek, or geo?  Are they different?
Key.InvDesc: A shiny, cast key adorned with a replica Hallownest Seal. Probably valuable to collectors.
Key.UsedInvDesc: May his sacrifice never be forgotten.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A spongy door reinforced with shards of old charms.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
At last, he'll be free to fulfill his destiny.
Insert the Fragile Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A spongy door reinforced with shards of old charms.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Mind your legs.
Insert the Fragile Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Don't let the Better Bugsness Bureau know about this.
Key.InvDesc: It glistens with gold, brighter than it should be. Don't break it.
Key.UsedInvDesc: He is free now to fulfill his destiny. Was it worth it?

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: The fungus grows ever onwards, without memory.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
An ascension to normalcy awaits.
Insert the Fungal Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: The fungus grows ever onwards, without memory.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The pilgrim's way expands.
Insert the Fungal Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Chop 'em, sautee 'em, stick 'em in a stew.

Key.UsedInvDesc: The wastes are opened, the Pilgrim's Way expands.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A lush door tainted with chains. This is a protected place.

The gardens must be tended.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A thickly grown door, wrapped in chains.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Hopefully you brought acid armor.
Insert the Garden Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Interesting to see things so cared for in a kingdom forgotten.
Key.InvDesc: A key draped in moss, tainted with infection.
Key.UsedInvDesc: May the sanctity of her garden never be broken.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A crystalline door, ravaged with chips and scratch marks.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
What was kept inside is long gone, surely the mountain is safe now.
Insert the Heart Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A dense, deeply crystallized door. It seems to have a heartbeat.

The heart of the mountain beckons.
Insert the Heart Key?

Key.UsedInvDesc: The mountain seems less whole for it, but surely it was for good.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: It's made of honeycombs, sturdy as stone.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The buzzing resonates with your soul.
Insert the Hive Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: The honey obscures a great darkness beyond.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The buzzing finally begins to fade.
Insert the Hive Key?

Key.ShopDesc: It's technically edible, I wouldn't recommend that though.
Key.InvDesc: A crystal of honey glued to an arsenal of stingers. It is difficult to hold.
Key.UsedInvDesc: They did not welcome you, but the queen understands.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A bright green door, bubbling with life. Don't touch it, though.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
It sizzles with a forgotten life.
Insert Isma's Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A bright green door, sizzling and rippling.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The flow weakens, aging and drying.
Insert Isma's Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Why does this smell like beetle dung?

Key.UsedInvDesc: Life must go on.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A heavy stone door bespeckled in forbidden fruit.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
Doomes is he who partakes of the forbidden.
Insert Joni's Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A robust door overgrown with lifeblood.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
You weren't invited, but you're here anyway.
Insert Joni's Key?

Key.ShopDesc: I feel like I shouldn't have this, so it's at a discount.

Key.UsedInvDesc: It was not yours to take, but it will be put to good use.
Key.Logic: (Fungus1_28[left1] | Fungus1_28[left2] + (RIGHTDASH | RIGHTSUPERDASH | WINGS | SHADESKIPS | LEFTCLAW + RIGHTCLAW + OBSCURESKIPS)) + LEFTBALDURS

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A creaking door, rusting and rotting. It smells of infestation.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
A great shadow looms beyond.
Insert the Junk Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A creaking door, rusting and rotting. It smells of infestation.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
An unconscionable chanting grows in the distance.
Insert the Junk Key?

Key.ShopDesc: It comes with complimentary uncaged Lumaflies.
Key.InvDesc: A dirty key embedded with the paltriest of geo, worth less than its weight.
Key.UsedInvDesc: ...what have you done?

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A large, wet door, lit by refractions from the lake.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
An uncomfortably welcoming laughter seeps through the cracks.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A wet, quiet door. There is a certain shadow about it.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
You sense the sadness of a journey completed.
Insert the Lake Key?

Key.ShopDesc: Many souls died to use this key, I assume that makes it worth this price.
Key.InvDesc: A shell of blue encases the metal, which seems to always reflect a dancing light.
Key.UsedInvDesc: What will you do now, that the mystery is solved?

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A sharp, carefully sculpted door. It smells of honor.

Your challengers await.
Insert the Mantis Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A great door of warrior's pride.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
You can come back later, with a sharper nail.
Insert the Mantis Key?

Key.ShopDesc: It unlocks one of the most guarded places in the kingdom.
Key.InvDesc: Polished, sharp, emblazoned with a proud insignia. A warrior's key.
Key.UsedInvDesc: Your respect is earned.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A crystallized door echoing of light and song.
LeftLocation.KeyDesc:
The purgatorial chaos of transition rando beckons.
Insert the Miner's Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A crystallized door echoing of light and song.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The call of the mines reigns out.
Insert the Miner's Key?

Key.ShopDesc: A precious little soul. Such a shame...
Key.InvDesc: A delicate key filled with spirit. It gleams with a twinkle of orange light.
Key.UsedInvDesc: Damned are those who prey on innocence.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A lush door, smothered in moss. It's almost hidden.

The power of leftslash compels you.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A lush door, overgrown in moss. It's wiggling, slightly?

The forgotten god awaits.
Insert the Moss Key?

Key.UsedInvDesc: You didn't go there without vertical, did you?

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: It looks like you can't get any closer, ghost.

It looks like you found a way to get closer.
Insert the Mothwing Key?

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: Are you scared, ghost? You should be.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
She'll be stronger next time.

Key.ShopDesc: You too can unlock your inner SHAAAW

You can feel your skin crawling.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A silken door, trapping in the darkness.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The luscious babble of repose calls from the other side.

Key.ShopDesc: I tried cleaning it but it always seems to have more webs.

Key.UsedInvDesc: Greater thorns await within.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A buried door, overgrown with the lush of the canyon.

It's okay, you have an excuse this time.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A buried door, overgrown with the lush of the canyon.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The pilgrim's way awaits your return.

Key.ShopDesc: Strange... this key seems like it's been forgotten more times than anyone can remember.

Key.UsedInvDesc: There was nothing here but a scream.

The screech of saw blades permeates all.

RightLocation.KeyDesc:
The screech of saw blades permeates all.

LeftLocation.NoKeyDesc: A regal door glowing with soul, awaiting a student.

A pure focus awaits.

It has been too long in the study, after all.

Key.UsedInvDesc: So much was sacrificed in vain.

The abyss knows no bottom.

The destiny of darkness awaits.

The path of the warrior ends here.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: The door of a rival, a betrayor, guarding her keep.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Perhaps betrayal was never the way.

Even the King's influence does not reach here.

RightLocation.NoKeyDesc: A solid door reinforced with silk weaves.
RightLocation.KeyDesc:
Are you sure this is the right way?

Key.ShopDesc: I think this is technically an heirloom? I should probably charge more for it.
